channel.title: [317] S Client [/317]
channel.description:
Well I have been working on this client for quite a while now and I decided to release it to help people progress on their servers. You can also connect to my server via this client but that can be changed easily on the GUI that pops up once it is ran.
Features: 377 cache Perfect skillcapes and hoods perfect void new perfect firecape ints rune defender, torso godswords and tassets and stuff with perfect ints some new custom interfaces helpful guis and guides within the client pest control interface along with some obvious 377 stuff
Pictures coming soon
http://www.mediafire.com/?sharekey=1771fb46d3a32b19d9d5c56d04dfa8b0e04e75f6e8ebb871
Enjoy :D
Enjoy, feedback would be appreciated.
